data.description: Rockford 5 bed, 4 bath, 2 story home on a corner 1/2 acre fenced in lot! The home features a main floor with nice sized kitchen, dining, living rooms along with a family room that has beautiful double sided fireplace. Upper level has 4 bedrooms, a full bath and a primary suite. Please note this home is priced with the knowledge of deferred maintenance. A great opportunity to build quick equity.
